WEBVTT

01:38.000 --> 01:41.000
I recognized her

01:41.000 --> 01:45.000
I was about eight years old, 

01:46.000 --> 01:48.000
and we used to play with her.

01:48.000 --> 01:50.000
Eat, eat…

01:54.000 --> 02:00.000
I told the other kids: “She's going to be my wife”.

02:02.000 --> 02:05.000
And that turned out to be true!

03:44.000 --> 03:46.000
Bye my love, be safe

03:46.000 --> 03:49.000
and defend yourself from the goat.

03:49.000 --> 03:52.000
If the goat comes here,

03:52.000 --> 03:55.000
go inside quickly because the goat could attack you.

03:56.000 --> 04:01.000
As soon as you see it, go inside and stay there, ok?

04:29.000 --> 04:36.000
Violence ended everything, ended with the town

04:41.000 --> 04:44.000
All the good atmosphere. Everything was pretty.

04:50.000 --> 04:54.000
Beautiful houses, 
small but beautiful houses.

04:57.000 --> 05:00.000
Good atmosphere.

05:00.000 --> 05:04.000
When it all ended, It was the '48,

05:04.000 --> 05:06.000
it happened suddenly,

05:06.000 --> 05:09.000
they exchanged gunfire from that hill

05:09.000 --> 05:12.000
to this hill and there, from the cliff.

05:15.000 --> 05:18.000
And then the people, those who didn't die,

05:18.000 --> 05:22.000
they left from here, to far away,

05:22.000 --> 05:26.000
they left and went away, leaving their lands behind,

05:26.000 --> 05:29.000
abandoned.

05:30.000 --> 05:36.000
Bullets from rifles are still found.

05:38.000 --> 05:43.000
over there in the cemetery, 
the workers covered up 7 rifle hits.

05:43.000 --> 05:46.000
There are gunshots, even in the dead.

05:47.000 --> 05:50.000
There are still these crosses. 

05:51.000 --> 06:00.000
Here, this one is from a certain "Patiño", 
who was killed there, on that hill. They killed him.

06:00.000 --> 06:05.000
The man was killed when he was going to Bucaramanga,

06:05.000 --> 06:10.000
he was riding a horse daily, 
at that time there was no road, 

06:10.000 --> 06:14.000
he was traveling with another gentleman...

06:29.000 --> 06:32.000
- Don Guillermo, come a minute!

06:39.000 --> 06:42.000
- Why does Mrs. María always stay here alone?

06:42.000 --> 06:49.000
- Because she can't see. Last night...
Last night I gave her the food,

06:49.000 --> 06:52.000
and she couldn’t see where the food was.

06:52.000 --> 06:54.000
No, she couldn't see.

06:54.000 --> 07:01.000
That's why after it gets dark, I take her inside.

07:01.000 --> 07:04.000
-So she can lay down and rest.
- Yes.

07:04.000 --> 07:07.000
- Why are you afraid of the goat ?

07:07.000 --> 07:09.000
An animal like that can hit you with a big blow

07:09.000 --> 07:13.000
and then take you away.

07:13.000 --> 07:16.000
That crazy man over there in the town,

07:16.000 --> 07:20.000
Have you seen him? He always 
walks with his hands like this. 

07:21.000 --> 07:24.000
- Oh yes, Lucho?

07:24.000 --> 07:28.000
He's is that way because of a camuro (goat) that hit him.

07:28.000 --> 07:30.000
- Did it hit him?

07:30.000 --> 07:34.000
- Yes, he gave him a hit and knocked him down.

07:34.000 --> 07:37.000
The “camuro” (goat) that hit him. 

