Sometimes I talk to her, at night, 
and ask her if she remembers

09:59.520 --> 10:05.000
when she was about nine or ten years old, 
and if she remembers, 

10:05.520 --> 10:09.760
those were happy times

10:11.760 --> 10:15.840
but everything comes and passes and everything ends.

