10:27.840 --> 10:30.000
She had seven surgeries on her head, 

10:30.840 --> 10:36.000
and that's why she lost her speech 
because they cut the brain tissues, 

10:36.960 --> 10:43.960
and then she couldn't speak. I went to see her,

10:43.960 --> 10:47.520
in the bed where she was, she spent four years there, 

10:47.960 --> 10:50.520
lying in a hospital bed, and I spent exactly four years there,

10:50.520 --> 10:54.800
in the hospital with her, in Bucaramanga. 

10:54.800 --> 10:59.800
Nurses wanted to take me out. No, I'm not leaving here because

10:59.800 --> 11:06.600
once I take my wife out, I'm going with her, 
they won't take me out of here. 

11:06.600 --> 11:12.120
They had shaved her entire head so I asked a nurse: 

11:12.120 --> 11:16.120
“how is her hair going to grow back?”  
She said:  “I have a shampoo,

11:16.120 --> 11:22.240
I'm going to give you one so you can apply it

11:22.240 --> 11:27.240
on her little head every day, and her hair will grow back

11:27.240 --> 11:32.320
in eight days, new hair will start growing, you’ll see”.

